divs: Sighting DetailsAbout 7:15 PM.I let my dogs outside and noticed 2 bright yellow lights in the eastern sky.At first I thought maybe with clear sky and almost full moon maybe it was a couple of planets , or maybe one planet and a star. Then I thought it shouldn't be pulsating .So I came in the house to get my husdband, and i looked back thru the window and the first one was gone then the second dimmed out, and was gone.There was no sound, but they were pretty far away.
